OL,5,G2300 The American Revolution
OL,6,     F2/6. George Washington takes
OL,7,     Fcommand of the Continental Army
OL,8,     Fand joins New England's fight to
OL,9,     Fliberate Boston. Congress declares
OL,10,     FAmerican independence.
OL,11,G0000 Heatwave
